---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Mind Planet">
  <main class="min-h-screen pt-24 pb-16 px-6 bg-background">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <a href="/terms-of-service-kr" class="text-sm px-3 py-1 bg-surface text-muted rounded-full hover:text-foreground transition-colors">KR</a>
          <a href="/terms-of-service-en" class="text-sm px-3 py-1 bg-primary/20 text-primary rounded-full">EN</a>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">Effective: July 1, 2025</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="space-y-12 text-foreground-muted leading-relaxed">

        <!-- Article 1 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 1 (Purpose)</h2>
          <p>These Terms establish rights, obligations, and responsibilities between Playke Inc. and users regarding the emotion-logging app "Mind Planet."</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 2 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 2 (Non-Medical Service Notice)</h2>
          <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 rounded-xl p-6 space-y-3">
            <p class="text-foreground font-medium">The Service is not medical and does not provide professional medical advice, diagnosis, treatment, or prescriptions.</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
              <li>Information provided is for general information and self-reflection only, not a substitute for qualified professionals.</li>
              <li>Users should consult professionals before making health-related decisions.</li>
              <li>In emergencies or crises, users should contact emergency numbers or crisis hotlines immediately, not rely on this Service.</li>
              <li>Mind Planet is not a certified medical device and does not provide professional counseling.</li>
              <li>AI responses are automatically generated and may be inaccurate.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 3 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 3 (Definitions)</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
              <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">"Service"</p>
              <p>The mobile application "Mind Planet" recording and analyzing emotions and thoughts</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
              <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">"User"</p>
              <p>Any person using the Service</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
              <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">"Paid Service"</p>
              <p>Additional subscription or separately paid features</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
              <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">"Basic User"</p>
              <p>Users installing the app without sign-up</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
              <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">"Subscriber"</p>
              <p>Users accessing server-based features through paid subscription</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 4 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 4 (Effect and Amendments)</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Terms take effect when posted in the Service or app store page.</li>
            <li>The Company may amend Terms within applicable law with prior notice.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 5 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 5 (Conclusion and Termination of Agreement)</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>For Basic Users, agreement forms upon app installation without sign-up.</li>
            <li>For Paid Services, agreement forms upon payment completion.</li>
            <li>Users may stop using the Service anytime; subscription cancellation follows app store policies.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 6 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 6 (Service Contents and Conditions)</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">The Service provides:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mb-4">
            <li>Emotion logging and analysis</li>
            <li>AI-based feedback</li>
            <li>Emotion statistics</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5 space-y-2">
            <p><span class="text-primary">Basic Users:</span> Store records locally</p>
            <p><span class="text-primary">Subscribers:</span> Store records on servers via anonymous authentication</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-3">Server-based features are available during subscription periods only. The Company may modify the Service for operational or technical reasons.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 7 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 7 (Subscriptions and Fees)</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Paid Services are offered as monthly or yearly subscriptions or per-session products.</li>
            <li>Prices, payment terms, and refund rules follow separate notices within the Service.</li>
            <li>The Company may change prices without prior notice; changes don't apply to existing subscribers.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 8 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 8 (Refunds and Cancellation)</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
              <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">Full Refund</p>
              <p>Within 7 days of subscription with no usage</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
              <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">Partial Refund</p>
              <p>After deducting regular prices for months used</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm">Discounted annual plans may have no or partial refunds. Refunds process under app store policies.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 9 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 9 (User Rights and Obligations)</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Users must use the Service properly and shall not:</p>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2">
            <p>Steal information</p>
            <p>Attempt unauthorized access or attacks on servers</p>
            <p>Conduct unrelated commercial activities</p>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm">Users are responsible for backing up and securing their own data. Paid users should monitor subscription status and auto-renewal.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 10 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 10 (Company's Obligations)</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>The Company endeavors to provide continuous and stable Service</li>
            <li>Implements technical and administrative measures to protect personal and record data</li>
            <li>May temporarily suspend Service for maintenance or emergencies with notice</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 11 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 11 (Personal Data and Records)</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p>The Company collects minimal personal data and uses anonymous authentication for paid features.</p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
                <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">Basic Users</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Data stores only on devices; the Company doesn't store or view it on servers.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-5">
                <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2">Subscribers</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Data stores on servers via anonymous authentication; the Company doesn't view such data.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 12 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 12 (Service Termination and Agreement Cancellation)</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>The Company may terminate the Service for unavoidable reasons with at least 30 days' notice.</li>
            <li>Users may stop and delete the Service anytime; deleting the app removes all local data.</li>
            <li>Server-stored data may be deleted within a certain period after subscription expiry.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Article 13 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">Article 13 (Dispute Resolution and Governing Law)</h2>
          <p>These Terms are governed by Republic of Korea laws. Disputes resolve through mutual consultation; failing that, the competent court is Seoul Central District Court.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <section class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <p class="mb-2"><span class="text-foreground-muted">Contact:</span> <span class="text-foreground">melo@playke.app</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-foreground-muted">Company:</span> <span class="text-foreground">Playke, Seoul, Korea</span></p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <!-- Back to home -->
      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-border">
        <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:underline">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
